title: Finding.Nemo[2003]DvDrip[Eng]-CIA
description: Marlin (a clown fish) is a widower who only has his son Nemo left of his family after a predator attack. Years later, on Nemo&#039;s first day of school, he&#039;s captured by a scuba diver and taken to live in a dentist office&#039;s fish tank. Marlin and his new absent-minded friend Dory set off across the ocean to find Nemo, while Nemo and his tankmates scheme on how to get out of the tank before he becomes the dentist&#039;s niece&#039;s new pet.
